      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INDIAN RUPEE (1) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a 2 length third over 520m at Q Parklands, clocking 30.54. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to her name from 10 starts. Capable of going well again. TUTA PEBBLES (4) latest effort finished 6th in a Free For All on March 27 over 390m at this track behind GOLDSTAR SUMMER beaten 4.5 lengths (22.35). With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts GOLDSTAR SUMMER (7) has shown good improvement at her last two starts, the latest scoring at this track over 390m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Can make it two on the bounce. FEDERAL EMERAN (8) did a good job to finish third last time out over 390m at this track (22.25) in a Free For All, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
